				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "READ IN FULL, YOU HAVE TO SCROLL DOWN:\r\n\r\nVB that plays after DEN_RaidingParty_Confrontation. The dialog ends either with peace having been achieved or with one leader being knocked out by either the opposing leader or a player.\r\n\r\nThis VB has a greeting for each outcome, but there really are three main categories: Player punched a leader, the leaders punched each other OR piece was achieved.\r\n\r\nRequires two speakers.\r\n\r\nSpeaker 1 is the player who was in the Confrontation dialog, and as such may have punched one of the leaders.\r\n\r\nSpeaker 2 is an accompanying character and as such may be opinionated."
				}
			}
